<br>
Me-L58 epic mage, PoG robe, bracers, crown, etc. No BO3 legs tho(bad luck)<br>
<br>
Been at the JP gnolls for 10AA points now. I can make 1 - 1.5 AA point per KEI there(depends on how many i'm letting leech xp), and have PLvled some of my RL friends from 40 - 46 there. <br>
<br>
With epic &amp; KEI and minimal burning, i do 13gnolls before they repop. If i have 42 wiz or 41 cleric friend with me, we go thru about 17 before repop. <br>
<br>
i NEVER reclaim. Load up bubba with plate, full focus gear, daggers, defender. He kin go thru 2 or 3 before he's in need of a heal. I nuke sporadically, if bubba is hurting or i want to clear a few quick. Pull with L1 nuke, send pet, sit down, heal when necessary. <br>
<br>
Great AA xp, great loot, great PLvling for lower buddies, easy &amp; laid back. Only had to gate from train once (1) in 10AA points.<br>
<br>
Oh, if yer on prexus, THIS SPOT IS MINE!!! heheheh<br>
<br>
